snippet.title: A Long Road Home - Steam Anniversary Trailer
snippet.description:
It was a little over a year ago, when A Long Road Home, our point and click adventure game made its debut on Steam. 

If you like mysteries, challenging puzzles and intriguing stories, don't miss out on this adventure:

http://store.steampowered.com/app/576160/A_Long_Road_Home/
